Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.65,1:42:10.60,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}发生了什么？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What just happened?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.75,1:42:11.93,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}那艘船一分为二{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The ship just split in two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.15,1:42:15.26,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}一艘往东飞去了 另一艘向南半球去了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Track one is heading east, track two to the southern hemisphere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.49,1:42:18.16,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 速度有多快？ - 接近...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- How fast is that bogey moving?       - Approaching...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.16,1:42:19.61,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}24马赫 并且还在加速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...Mach 24 and accelerating.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.83,1:42:22.90,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}看起来像是要降落在南印度洋的某个地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's gonna impact somewhere in the Indian Ocean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.22,1:42:42.86,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}另一艘船也在降落{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The rest of the ship is descending.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.85,1:42:45.22,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}荧幕显示{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Put it on the board now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.22,1:42:46.29,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}遵命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.32,1:42:48.50,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}天啊{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.00,1:43:31.77,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}让幽灵引擎待命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Bring the phantom drive online.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.39,1:43:55.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}已经与世界引擎建立连接{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We are now slave to the world engine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.96,1:43:58.37,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}启动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Initiate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.63,1:44:33.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他们发射过来的是什么？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What have they hit us with?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.67,1:44:35.84,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3} 看上去像是某种重力武器{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Looks like some kind of gravity...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.10,1:44:39.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}和他们的飞船同步工作{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...weapon. It's working in tandem with their ship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.07,1:44:43.14,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}一种可以增加地球质量的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Somehow they're increasing the Earth's mass...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.41,1:44:45.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}利用微尘污浊大气{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...clouding the atmosphere with particulates.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.24,1:44:48.85,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}天哪{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.18,1:44:51.88,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他们在进行环境改造{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're terraforming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.95,1:44:52.76,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}那是什么？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.58,1:44:54.69,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}行星工程{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Planetary engineering...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.95,1:44:58.16,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}修改地球上的大气和地形{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...modifying the Earth's atmosphere and topography.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.42,1:44:59.66,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他们要把地球转化成氪星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Turning Earth into Krypton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.36,1:45:03.50,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 但是我们会怎么样？ - 理论上说...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- But what happens to us?       - Based on these readings...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.76,1:45:06.76,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 不再有"我们"了    - 斯旺威克将军{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- ...there won't be an "us."       - General Swanwick, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.16,1:45:08.54,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}控制塔来电{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm on with the control tower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.80,1:45:11.64,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}哈迪上校正在路上 和他在一起的还有超人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Colonel Hardy's on his way and he's got Superman in tow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.77,1:45:12.84,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}超人？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Superman?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.37,1:45:14.54,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}那个外星人 先生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The alien, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.80,1:45:17.18,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他们叫他超人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's what they're calling him. Superman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.68,1:45:23.88,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们有个计划 将军{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We have a plan, general.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.15,1:45:26.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}和我想的一样吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Is that what I think it is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.78,1:45:28.56,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}这是他坐的飞船{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's the ship he arrived in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.22,1:45:32.86,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}这艘飞船由某种叫幽灵引擎的物质驱动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This ship is powered by something called a phantom drive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.12,1:45:34.57,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}它能够扭曲时空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It bends space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.82,1:45:38.80,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}佐德的飞船运用了同样的原理 如果我们能让两者对撞{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Zod's ship uses the same technology, and if we can make the two drives collide...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.03,1:45:40.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}就能创造出一个奇异点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A singularity can be created.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.13,1:45:42.57,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 就像黑洞   - 对{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Like a black hole.       - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.70,1:45:44.20,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}所以如果我们打开通道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So if we open up this doorway...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.47,1:45:46.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}理论上来说他们就应该被吸进去{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...they should be pulled back in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.34,1:45:48.84,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}所以你想我们用那个炸掉他们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So you want us to bomb them with that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.07,1:45:51.05,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}将军 如果太空船达到{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}General, that craft maxes out...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.31,1:45:54.69,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}17000磅 可以从C-17投掷下来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...17,000 pounds, we can drop it from a C-17.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.91,1:45:56.05,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}这是可行的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's a viable plan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.31,1:45:58.42,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}如果我不阻止印度洋上的机器{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If I don't stop that machine over the Indian Ocean...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.68,1:46:02.30,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}重力场还会继续扩大{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...the gravity field will continue to expand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.76,1:46:10.53,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}如果那个东西是使地球氪星化{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If that thing is making Earth more like Krypton...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.89,1:46:12.93,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你在它附近不会更脆弱吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...won't you be weaker around it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.23,1:46:15.54,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}有可能{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Maybe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.40,1:46:18.88,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}但我不会让它阻止我试一试{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm not about to let that stop me from trying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.84,1:46:22.04,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你可能想后退一点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You might want to step back a little bit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.11,1:46:25.94,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}可能要再退一点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Maybe a little bit more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.71,1:46:58.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}芙拉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Faora.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.31,1:47:00.41,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你来指挥{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Take command.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.64,1:47:03.78,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 遵命   - 我要保证始源室的安全{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Yes, sir.       - I need to secure the genesis chamber...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.21,1:47:06.96,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}还要向一个老朋友致意{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and pay my respects to an old friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.72,1:47:16.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}守护者前往大都会{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Guardian en route to Metropolis...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.63,1:47:18.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}携带包裹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...package in tow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.10,1:47:27.01,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}被告知了F-35战机入境的会合点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Be advised, F-35s inbound to rendezvous point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.27,1:47:29.44,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你现在应该在视觉接触{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You should have visual contact now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.45,1:48:18.13,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}主控钥匙识别正确 始源室待命 先生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Command key accepted. Genesis chamber coming online, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.52,1:48:19.52,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}住手 佐德{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Stop this, Zod...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.69,1:48:21.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}趁还有时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...while there's still time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.06,1:48:26.37,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}还没放弃对我说教呢 是吧 哪怕是死了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Haven't given up lecturing me, have you, even in death?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.73,1:48:28.73,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我不会让你用密典做这些{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I will not let you use the Codex like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.00,1:48:30.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你没权力阻止我{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You don't have the power to stop me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.97,1:48:34.00,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我插入的主控钥匙已经废除了你的权限{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The command key I have entered is revoking your authority.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.24,1:48:37.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}飞船在我掌控之下了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This ship is now under my control.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.67,1:49:10.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}北方司令部 这里是闪电1号{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Northcom, Lightning 1, request...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.51,1:49:12.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}请求释放导弹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...permission to unleash the hounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.03,1:49:16.62,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}周围安全 可以袭击 可能的话发生作战损坏评估{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Lightning 1, you are clear to engage. Send battle damage assessment when able. Out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.19,1:49:32.57,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}电子设备陷入混乱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Avionics are going haywire. The gravity field...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.80,1:49:35.14,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}重力场牵引我们的导弹下坠 我们需要更加接近目标{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...is pulling our missiles down. We gotta get closer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.24,1:49:41.44,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}好了各位{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All right, everybody...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.54,1:49:44.42,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们离开了 现在就离开大楼{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...we're leaving. We're leaving the building now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.56,1:50:09.44,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我失去了我的僚机驾驶员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I just lost my wingman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.80,1:50:12.94,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}飞机失控 飞机失控 飞机失控{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Mayday! Mayday! Mayday!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.51,1:50:26.49,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}各位 这边{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Everybody, this way! Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.75,1:50:29.82,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}各位 快点 快 快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Everybody, come on! Keep moving, keep moving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.66,1:50:37.69,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}詹妮{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Jenny!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.66,1:50:42.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}天哪{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.76,1:50:43.77,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}玛丽{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Perry!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.20,1:50:50.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}走这边 快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Go! There! Go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.01,1:50:57.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们可以共存{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Our people can co-exist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.15,1:51:00.12,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}这样我们就像你儿子那样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So we can suffer through years of pain{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.12,1:51:02.65,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}撑过数年的伤痛来适应环境？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}trying to adapt like your son has?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.99,1:51:04.66,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 你说的是种族屠杀   - 是的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- You're talking about genocide.       - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.89,1:51:07.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}而且我正和一个鬼魂争论其功过{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And I'm arguing its merits with a ghost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.86,1:51:10.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们都是鬼魂 佐德{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're both ghosts, Zod.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.89,1:51:14.40,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你不明白吗？你不愿放弃的氪星已经没了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Can't you see that? The Krypton you're clinging onto is gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.66,1:51:17.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你检查好入侵的情报了吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Ship, have you managed to quarantine this invasive intelligence?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.50,1:51:18.42,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 失败了   - 好了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- You'll fail.        - I have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.63,1:51:20.05,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}准备好终结这一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Then prepare to terminate it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.30,1:51:22.08,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我不想争吵了 让我闭嘴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm tired of this debate. Silencing me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.34,1:51:23.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}改变不了任何事{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...won't change anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.01,1:51:27.32,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我儿子...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}My son...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.14,1:51:29.49,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}比你强两倍{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...is twice the man you were.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.48,1:51:34.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他会结束我们发起的种种{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And he will finish what we started.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.08,1:51:36.32,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我保证{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I can promise you that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.52,1:51:42.90,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}告诉我{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Tell me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.16,1:51:46.73,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你有乔•艾尔的记忆和良知{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...you have Jor-El's memories, his conscience.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.43,1:51:50.20,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}可你经历过他的痛苦吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Can you experience his pain?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.87,1:51:55.44,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我会从你儿子的尸体里提取密典{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I will harvest the Codex from your son's corpse...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.90,1:52:01.21,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}在他的尸骨之上重建氪星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and I will rebuild Krypton atop his bones.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.63,1:52:59.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}詹妮{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Jenny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.60,1:53:02.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 詹妮 詹妮 你在哪？ - 我在这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Jenny. Jenny, where are you?       - I'm here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.60,1:53:03.90,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 这里 这里   - 詹妮{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I'm here. Here.       - Jenny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.91,1:53:05.41,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}撑住 撑住{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hold on, hold on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.64,1:53:06.62,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我卡住了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm stuck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.84,1:53:08.52,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 我动不了 卡住了   - 好的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I can't get free. I'm stuck.       - Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.78,1:53:11.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们会把你救出去 你别动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We'll get you out of there, all right? Just sit tight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.58,1:53:12.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不不{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No, no, no!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.41,1:53:14.22,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 别离开我   - 我不会离开你{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Don't leave me.       - We're not gonna leave you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.35,1:53:15.52,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 好   - 伦巴第{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Okay.       - Lombard!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.78,1:53:19.13,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 他妈的快过来帮忙   - 该死{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Get your ass over here and help me.       - Damn it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.12,1:53:23.10,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 用这个撬   - 给你{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- We just gotta move this.       - Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.33,1:53:25.36,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}用力试试看 好了吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Slide that in. You push, I'll pull, okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.63,1:53:26.66,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}来吧{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.87,1:53:32.17,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 用力   - 天啊{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Push!       - Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.43,1:53:34.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}越来越近了 用力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's getting closer! Come on, push!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.10,1:53:38.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}北方司令部 这里是守护者 可以投掷吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Northcom, this is Guardian. Are we cleared?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.84,1:53:39.84,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不行 守护者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Negative, Guardian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.57,1:54:07.01,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}快 用力啊{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Come on! Push!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.02,1:55:00.36,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他做到了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He did it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.56,1:55:03.80,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}北方司令部 这里是守护者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Northcom, this is Guardian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.06,1:55:06.30,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们正经过调整线 一切良好{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're passing through phase line red. Good to go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.56,1:55:07.73,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}一路平安 守护者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Godspeed, Guardian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.73,1:55:10.14,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}整理包裹 准备投掷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Arm the package. You are cleared hot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.40,1:55:12.47,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}准备发出最后一击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're lining up for the final run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.27,1:55:15.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}现在看你和汉密尔顿的了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's up to you and Hamilton now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.44,1:55:56.44,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}搞什么{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You gotta be kidding me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.45,1:55:59.30,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}理货员 包裹是否武装完毕？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Loadmaster, is the package ready to drop?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.35,1:56:00.62,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不行 守护者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Negative, Guardian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.85,1:56:02.42,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}出问题了 不该这样的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There's something wrong. It's not supposed to do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.65,1:56:04.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}那应该怎样？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What's it supposed to do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.65,1:56:07.69,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 应该完全插进去   - 我看看{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- It's supposed to go in all the way.       - Let me take a look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.96,1:56:09.53,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}副驾驶接管飞机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Co-pilot's aircraft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.26,1:56:11.76,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}副驾驶接管飞机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Co-pilot's aircraft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.50,1:56:21.17,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们已经排列好准备投掷了 还在等什么？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We are lined up for the drop. What's the hold up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.44,1:56:22.44,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}出现了点问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We've had a setback.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.19,1:56:39.69,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}瞄准飞机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Target that aircraft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.56,1:56:45.00,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}锁定目标{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Target locked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.80,1:56:55.68,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不要{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Stop!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.90,1:56:58.01,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}如果你毁了这艘飞船{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If you destroy this ship...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.24,1:57:00.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}就是毁了氪星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...you destroy Krypton!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.71,1:57:05.89,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}氪星本来还有机会的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Krypton had its chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.87,1:58:01.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}莲恩小姐 这儿不安全{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Miss Lane! It's not safe for you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.97,1:58:02.88,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}离开那儿{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...over there!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.10,1:58:03.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}莲恩小姐{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Miss Lane!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.60,1:58:35.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}离开 快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Move now! Go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.19,1:58:57.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}死得光荣{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A good death...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.46,1:58:59.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}就是死得其所{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...is its own reward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.49,2:00:02.93,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他们走了吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Are they gone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.09,2:00:05.50,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我想是的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.40,2:00:08.74,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他救了我们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He saved us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.22,2:00:37.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他们说初吻之后就每况愈下了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You know, they say it's all downhill after the first kiss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.90,2:00:43.93,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我很确定 他们只统计了亲吻人类的数据{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm pretty sure that only counts when you're kissing a human.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.29,2:01:14.77,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}看这个{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Look at this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.07,2:01:21.10,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们本可以在这片废墟上建立起一个新的氪星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We could have built a new Krypton in this squalor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.24,2:01:24.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}但是在我们和人类之间 你选择了后者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But you chose the humans over us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.77,2:01:27.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我的存在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I exist...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.58,2:01:29.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}仅是为了守护氪星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...only to protect Krypton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.75,2:01:35.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}这是自我出生以来的唯一目的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That is the sole purpose for which I was born.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.99,2:01:39.12,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我所做的一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And every action I take...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.35,2:01:41.36,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}无论多暴力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...no matter how violent...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.62,2:01:43.33,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}多么残忍{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...or how cruel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.53,2:01:49.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}皆是为了我的人民的福祉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...is for the greater good of my people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.43,2:01:54.85,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}现在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.10,2:01:57.38,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我没有人民了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...I have no people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.81,2:02:10.00,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}是你夺走了我的灵魂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}My soul that is what you have taken from me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.79,2:02:19.29,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我要让他们承担痛苦{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm going to make them suffer, Kal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.53,2:02:22.97,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你救下的人类 我要从你手里...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These humans you've adopted, I will take them all from you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.20,2:02:26.18,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 一个一个夺走   - 你这个怪物 佐德{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- ...one by one.       - You're a monster, Zod...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.80,2:02:30.61,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我会阻止你的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and I'm gonna stop you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.61,2:04:14.00,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}结束这一切只有一个办法{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There's only one way this ends, Kal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.14,2:04:15.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不是你死{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Either you die...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.24,2:04:17.52,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}就是我亡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...or I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.68,2:04:50.82,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我被当做一个战士训练{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I was bred to be a warrior, Kal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.68,2:04:55.70,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我终生都在受训控制感官{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Trained my entire life to master my senses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.88,2:04:59.49,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你在哪受训的？农场吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Where did you train? On a farm?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.42,2:07:12.80,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}如果你深爱着这群人类{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If you love these people so much...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.19,2:07:15.46,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}就为他们追悼吧{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...you can mourn for them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.93,2:07:21.00,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不要{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Don't do this!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.20,2:07:25.01,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}住手{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Stop!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.37,2:07:32.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Stop!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.71,2:07:35.85,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不可能{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Never.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.54,2:09:11.92,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你他妈是蠢蛋吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Are you effing stupid?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.14,2:09:14.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你有那么多空中侦察机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's one of your surveillance drones.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.11,2:09:16.61,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}这玩意值1200万{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's a $12,000,000 piece of hardware.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.78,2:09:17.81,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}曾经值{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.61,2:09:21.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我知道你想追踪我{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I know you're trying to find out where I hang my cape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.75,2:09:25.00,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 但是没门   - 那我明确问你一个问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- You won't.       - Then I'll ask the obvious question:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.22,2:09:28.82,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我们怎么知道有一天 你不会损害美国的利益？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}How do we know you won't one day act against America's interests?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.92,2:09:30.77,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我在堪萨斯长大 将军{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I grew up in Kansas, general.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.23,2:09:33.40,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我也算是美国人了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm about as American as it gets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.66,2:09:34.57,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}看{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Look...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.80,2:09:36.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我愿意帮忙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...I'm here to help...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.50,2:09:38.74,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}但必须是我心甘情愿{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...but it has to be on my own terms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.97,2:09:40.81,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你可以这样说服华盛顿{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have to convince Washington of that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.07,2:09:45.57,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}就算我愿意说 你认为他们会听吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even if I were willing to try, what makes you think they'd listen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.14,2:09:47.74,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}不知道 将军{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I don't know, general.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.14,2:09:50.85,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}但是我只能相信你{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Guess I'll just have to trust you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.42,2:10:03.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 你笑什么 上尉？  - 没什么 长官{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- What are you smiling about?       - Nothing, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.13,2:10:09.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我觉得他帅爆了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I just think he's kind of hot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.27,2:10:13.37,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 上车 上尉   - 遵命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Get in the car, captain.       - Mm-hm. Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.34,2:10:26.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他一直坚信你生来要做大事的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He always believed you were meant for greater things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:26.81,2:10:28.32,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}当这一天来临时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And that when the day came...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.55,2:10:31.36,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你的肩膀要能扛起千斤{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...your shoulders would be able to bear the weight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.62,2:10:35.47,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}是啊 我希望他能够看到这一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah, I just wish he could have been here to see it finally happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:35.89,2:10:38.47,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}他看到了 克拉克 相信我{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He saw it, Clark, believe me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.37,2:11:28.22,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你不拯救地球的时候 想干点什么？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What are you going to do when you're not saving the world?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.44,2:11:32.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 有想过吗？ - 想过 真的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Have you given any thought to that?       - I have, actually. Heh, heh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:33.78,2:11:37.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我会找一份工作 能够保持高度警觉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I gotta find a job where I can keep my ear to the ground.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.02,2:11:45.09,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}人们不会多看我两眼{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Where people won't look twice...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.36,2:11:49.14,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}当我要去危险的地方 不会问我问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...when I want to go somewhere dangerous and start asking questions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.24,2:12:06.28,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}行行好 露易丝 你什么时候能可怜我一下呢？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Come on, Lois. When are you gonna throw me a bone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.55,2:12:09.22,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}今晚比赛的绝佳位子 怎么样？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Courtside seats to the game tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.65,2:12:11.22,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 什么？ - 我说...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- What do you say?       - I say...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.45,2:12:13.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你应该去钓钓实习生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...you should go back to trolling the intern pool.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.26,2:12:17.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}可能会有好运 抱歉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You'll probably have more luck. Sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:19.43,2:12:20.10,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}看比赛？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Courtside?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.33,2:12:22.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 别去   - 不去{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Don't. Ha, ha, ha.       - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.30,2:12:25.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}伦巴第 莲恩 来见见新的特约通讯员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Lombard, Lane, I want you to meet our new stringer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:25.33,2:12:28.58,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}你给他传授传授窍门 他叫卡拉克•肯特{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I want you to show him the ropes. This is Clark Kent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.80,2:12:30.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}好运 孩子{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Good luck, kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.64,2:12:32.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我叫斯蒂夫{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hey. Steve.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.14,2:12:34.64,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}- 幸会   - 幸会{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Nice to meet you.       - You too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.64,2:12:35.48,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}嗨{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.41,2:12:37.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}我叫露易丝•莲恩{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Lois Lane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.58,2:12:40.12,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}欢迎来《星球日报》{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Welcome to the  Planet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:43.85,2:12:46.33,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\blur3}很高兴来这 露易丝{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Glad to be here, Lois.{\r}
